<div class="landing">
  <h1 class="title">  <%= t(".title") %>  </h1>
  <h2> <%= t(".full_title") %> </h2>
</div>
<div class="seconeexplain">
  <h3> <%= t(".description_header") %></h3>
  <p>Wether you want to exchange your items for cash or buy something unique, SUBS has got you covered!</p>
</div>
<section class="homesection1">
  <div class="subsdiagram">
    <h3>Buy</h3>
    <%= image_tag("/assets/homeinstruc.png", :alt => "rss feed") %>
  </div>
  <div class="subsdiagram">
    <h3>Sell</h3>
    <%= image_tag("/assets/subsBuy.jpg", :alt => "rss feed") %>
  </div>
</section>
<section class="homesection2">
  <div class="sectwoexplain">
    <h3>Whats so special about SUBS?</h3>
    <p>We believe in the power of second chances and new beginnings which is why our mission is to become Surrey Universitys most loved and trusted community of creators, buyers and sellers.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="uniqueSubs">
    <div class="textwhy">
      <h4>It's simple</h4>
      <p>SUBS has no listing fees, no selling fees. Students need every last penny they can get so we don't want to charge students to list their items</p>
    </div>
    <div class="textwhy">
      <h4>No to auctions</h4>
      <p>If you're buying or selling second hand, we offer a great alternative to the hassle and expense of auction sites.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="textwhy">
      <h4>Made for buyers and sellers</h4>
      <p>We are made for both buyers and sellers. So, whether you're wanting to find a new home for your unwanted items, or bag yourself a bargain, SUBS can help.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="textwhy">
      <h4>Good for the planet</h4>
      <p>Whether you're buying or selling, you're helping us on our mission to reduce landfill. Recycling is really important to SUBS, lets all do our bit.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
